item.title: Mutoh
item.description: Whatever wide format digital print solution you are looking for, Mutoh has it ! Quality is the thread that runs through every Mutoh wide format product. Mutoh offer wide format piezo drop on demand inkjet printers and sign cutting plotters for sign & display, specialty/industrial, dye sublimation & direct textile applications ! Source
